# --- myinventory: local config & scan output --------------------------------
# These describe your network (addresses, services, VMs) — keep them out of git.
# See docs/security.md.
# Default output dir holds inventory.json, the .d2 sources and any rendered
# diagrams (SVG/PNG). The test fixture under tests/fixtures/ is intentionally
# tracked and not matched here.
/myinventory.yaml
*.local.yaml
/out/

